        <span>üòä</span><span>üòÇ</span><span>‚ù§Ô∏è</span><span>üëç</span>
        <span>üôè</span><span>üòç</span><span>üéâ</span><span>üöÇ</span>
        <span>‚úÖ</span><span>üî•</span><span>üíØ</span><span>üëè</span>
      </div>
      
      <div class="chat-input-area">
        <button class="emoji-btn" id="emojiBtn">üòä</button>
